接近传统笔记本电脑。键盘是必不可少的，无论是键盘盒还是随身携带的蓝牙配件。一些键盘保护套，如苹果的 iPad 妙控键盘，内置触控板，这比在平板电脑屏幕上点击输入更符合人体工程学。此外，您可以更进一步，使用通过蓝牙连接到平板电脑的无线鼠标。如果您主要寻找平板电脑来替代笔记本电脑，请考虑购买<a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-2-in-1-laptops-for-2023-155052641.html">二合一笔记本电脑</a>，因为这些系统通常由高性能平板电脑组成，这些平板电脑设计用于（或不带）键盘。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/best-tablets-150026056.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-tablets-150026056.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 27194a7d-8435-4802-8ec0-3bfdb7d99cba</guid><dc:creator>萨姆卢瑟福</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 07 Jun 2023 20:15:06 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686168908</ingested><modified> 2023-06-07T20:15:16+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tablets]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sam Rutherford]]></category><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/a016ca50-9fc3-11ec-bfdd-f179728c5eac" width="1998"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/a016ca50-9fc3-11ec-bfdd-f179728c5eac" width="1998"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><