dai-for-negligence-in-wake-of-tiktok-car-thefts-192644446.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> efe9dd0c-57fa-42e3-b0fb-60d1dbd2f5ce</guid><dc:creator>肖恩·巴克利</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 07 Jun 2023 19:26:44 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686165833</ingested><modified> 2023-06-07T19:23:59+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[Crime & Justice]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sean Buckley]]></category><media:content height="3744" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-08/b24e34a0-eaa3-11ea-9ff9-3d67bfa315d8" width="5616"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3744" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-08/b24e34a0-eaa3-11ea-9ff9-3d67bfa315d8" width="5616"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[huettenhoelscher via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Nuremberg / Germany - April 7, 2019: Hyundai logo on a Hyundai car at a car dealer. The Hyundai Motor Company is a South Korean multinational automotive manufacturer headquartered in Seoul.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Hyundai logo on a Hyundai car at a car dealer]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best smart light bulbs for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>构建智能家居生态系统的最佳起点之一是智能灯泡。与其他物联网设备相比，它们不仅价格相对实惠，通常每个灯泡的价格在 10 到 50 美元之间，而且它们还可以彻底改变您家的感觉。您可以在几分钟内从无聊的模拟模式转变为丰富多彩的自动化模式，并且在使用智能灯泡创建色彩缤纷的灯光场景、设置时间表等方面有无限可能。</p><p>但与过去几年智能家居领域的其他领域一样，现在智能照明领域的参与者比以往任何时候都多。我们测试了市场上一些最流行的智能灯，发现大多数都很好，但在兼容性、色彩质量和移动应用程序可用性方面存在差异，在决定哪种智能灯泡系统适合之前值得考虑你家。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2>在智能灯泡中寻找什么</h2><h3>连通性（到集线器或不到集线器）</h3><p>智能灯的最大吸引力之一是能够通过手机控制它们。他们中的大多数人都可以通过 WiFi 或蓝牙连接到它，或者通过为他们处理连接的外部集线器来实现。蓝牙连接限制了您能够控制灯光的范围，因此它只适用于数量有限的灯泡和您不希望在外出时控制的灯泡。</p><p> WiFi 智能灯易于设置，并且总体上可以更便宜，因为它们不需要集线器来连接它们。但是，拥有中央 Zigbee 集线器之类的东西可以使您的整个系统更加可靠，因为它的连接与您家中的 WiFi 网络是分开的。出于这个原因，基于集线器的灯泡往往更具可扩展性，因此如果您希望最终在家中拥有数十个智能灯，我们主要推荐这些灯泡。</p><h3>白色还是彩色？</h3><p>今天你会发现的大多数智能灯泡都是“白色和彩色”灯泡，这意味着它们可以发出鲜艳的蓝色、粉色、绿色和介于两者之间的一切，还可以发出不同温度的白色。但也有一些只有白色的灯泡，而且它们通常比彩色灯泡更实惠。虽然我们建议为白色和彩色设备使用弹簧，但如果您只喜欢白色，请确保您获得的灯泡可以跨越色温范围（通常从 2000 到 5000 开尔文），为您提供各种级别温暖和凉爽的白光。</p><h3>应用功能</h3><p>智能灯的好处之一是您可以通过各种应用程序连接功能对它们进行控制。大多数配套应用程序可让您执行设置照明时间表、将单个灯分组到房间名称以及创建您自己的具有不同颜色的自定义灯光“场景”等操作。但是我们已经看到了其他功能，这些功能并不像假期模式那样普遍存在，可以自动打开和关闭灯以增强您的家庭安全，并与媒体同步，这会根据您正在收听的音乐或您当前正在直播的游戏。</p><h3>智能家居兼容性</h3><p>如果您经常使用亚马逊的 Alexa 或 Google Assistant 等智能助手，请确保您获得的智能灯能与您最喜欢的灯一起使用。我们测试的所有灯泡都支持亚马逊和谷歌的虚拟助手，允许您使用语音命令打开和关闭灯、调暗灯等等。这里的通配符是 Siri 和 Apple 的 HomeKit；虽然许多智能灯泡已将 HomeKit 添加到其兼容连接列表中，但并非所有灯都支持 Apple 的智能家居系统。</p><h3>可扩展性</h3><p>我们在上面提到了这一点，但您需要考虑最终需要在家中安装多少智能灯。一些品牌和照明系统比其他品牌和照明系统更容易扩展，如果您计划在家中的每个房间都安装智能灯，我们通常建议使用基于集线器的灯泡。如果您只是想用一些漂亮的灯装饰您的家庭办公室或客厅，WiFi 选项应该很适合您。值得庆幸的是，这些是您可以获得的一些最实惠的智能家居设备，所以即使您现在对这个问题没有明确的答案，如果您决定为您的家配备多个设备，您也可以重新考虑您的选择智能灯泡。</p><h2>最佳整体：飞利浦 Hue White + Color Ambiance </h2><p><core-commerce id="e665469b83be43b7b36503e801838eb9" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果您对智能灯做过任何研究，您可能遇到过<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQKLiQdjMORv95p41OUxPUt4jIe2cH5EvxXjRYP4fZ7j&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPhilips-Hue-Bluetooth-compatible-Assistant%2Fdp%2FB07QV9XB87">飞利浦 Hue 灯泡</a>。由于各种原因，该系列很受欢迎，我们同意它们是您可以获得的最好的智能灯泡，这要归功于它们广泛的兼容性、易于使用的移动应用程序和它们的可扩展性。特别是，如果您知道要为家中的多个房间配备这些物联网设备，飞利浦 Hue 是您的不二之选。</p><p>关于 Hue 灯泡，首先要了解的是它们现在支持蓝牙。这意味着您可以先购买一些进行试用，然后在您想为家中添加更多灯时使用集线器轻松扩展您的系统。以前，任何和所有灯都需要集线器，但现在在完全尝试之前将脚趾伸入范围内要容易得多。</p><p>与我们测试的所有其他智能灯一样，您只需拧上飞利浦 Hue 灯泡，打开灯，然后按照移动应用程序中的说明开始使用即可。即使您只有一个房间的灯开始，我们仍然建议在 Hue 应用程序中将它们分组到它们自己的“房间”中，这样​​您就可以轻松地同时控制整个空间的环境。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQKLiQdjMORv95p41OUxPUt4jIe2cH5EvxXjRYP4fZ7j&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPhilips-Hue-Bluetooth-compatible-Assistant%2Fdp%2FB07QV9XB87">Hue 的白色 + 彩色</a>灯泡提供一系列从暖到冷的白色和数百万种颜色供您在智能家居中进行试验。色彩丰富而充满活力，飞利浦的预编程场景，如活力、明亮和放松，让您可以快速模拟具有不同暖度白光的旧“哑”灯。您也可以从应用程序中的多种颜色场景中进行选择，但创建自己的色温也很容易。因此，如果您一直想在 Twitch 上直播时让您的办公室充满鲜艳的彩虹，您可以找到您想要的精确预设，保存它们，然后只需在应用程序。</p><p> Hue 应用程序非常易于使用，灯泡支持亚马逊 Alexa 和谷歌智能助理的语音命令。这意味着您甚至不必打开应用程序来控制您的灯光；你可以简单地使用语音控制并说“Alexa，关掉卧室的灯”，只有那个指定房间的灯会熄灭。仅使用蓝牙，您就可以向系统添加多达 10 个灯泡——此时您必须将飞利浦 Hue 集线器添加到组合中以支持多达 50 个灯。该集线器还支持 HomeKit 连接、灯光时间表和自动化、在家和外出模式以及与电影和音乐同步等功能。</p><p>可以说，这些功能中最有用的是自动化功能，它可以让您设置灯的开/关时间表，包括在您离开家时自动关灯。可以理解为什么飞利浦将这些少数功能专用于 Hue 集线器——将集线器添加到组合中可以使系统更可靠，允许您使用越来越多的连接灯做更多事情，而且它会鼓励许多人投资集线器随着时间的推移，还有更多的 Hue 灯泡。我们喜欢 Hue 的集线器，不仅因为它的可靠性，还因为它允许对您的设备进行更精细、更灵活的控制。因此，如果您正在度假并想打开客厅的灯以查看发生了什么，您可以这样做。</p><p>可扩展性超出了您在智能家居中拥有的灯的数量：它还包括多个可以安装在室外的智能灯泡。 Hue 系列有大量室内和室外灯泡可供选择，包括嵌入式灯、室外基座灯和泛光灯、灯带等。它是当今为数不多的几个系列之一，可以为您提供大量选择，让您家中的每个灯泡都变得智能，如果您知道自己想要全面投入智能灯前端，这一点很重要。</p><p>但这给我们带来了飞利浦 Hue 的最大缺点，那就是价格。 Hue 灯泡价格昂贵，两包 White + Color Ambiance 灯泡售价 80 美元。如果您正在寻找便宜的灯泡来测试智能照明，我们下面的一些其他首选，如 Kasa 智能灯泡，将是更好的选择，因为它们中的大多数每个灯泡的价格都较低。但是，如果您希望在未来投资智能照明，我们建议您使用飞利浦的 Hue 入门套件之一： <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9QaGlsaXBzLUh1ZS1TdGFydGVyLUNvbXBhdGlibGUtQXNzaXN0YW50L2RwL0IwOTVLUVNYWUg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZ3MtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImMxN2RkNDJhLTI3YzktNGViYy1iZGMwLTlhNDNjNmQyNGMwOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQL-pui21HZF1vUC5rEEgjkEBsX6zl4Zo8WKfF5yhXES&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPhilips-Hue-Starter-Compatible-Assistant%2Fdp%2FB095KQSXYH">White + Color Ambiance 入门套件</a>，包括三个灯泡、一个集线器和一个智能按钮，售价 180 美元，这比单独购买所有这些组件要便宜。</p><h2>亚军：LIFX Color A19 </h2><p><core-commerce id="a07c0747ccbb4b2094f9654dbff5fa13" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>总的来说，LIFX 的彩色智能灯与 Hue 的 White + Ambiance 灯泡相似，因为它们易于设置，提供醒目的饱和色彩，并适用于三个主要平台：Alexa、Google Assistant 和 HomeKit。但主要区别在于 LIFX 灯泡仅支持 WiFi，因此即使您愿意也无法将它们连接到集线器，而且有些灯泡比 Hue 设备稍微贵一些。支持 1100 流明的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUpzdy1WeA4afh2sFMK2BEeiGJRFluHCqPpYdT8uX1Wk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLIFX-Color-1100lm-Edison-Screw%2Fdp%2FB08BKXPX3N">Color A19 灯泡</a>通常售价 50 美元，但有一款<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAb-D7JUnuh6yQsZTmArpSNcRrz0jxJahwWcSXlTSY6s_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLIFX-Color-800lm-Edison-Screw%2Fdp%2FB08BL16M81%3F">800 流明的等效灯泡</a>要便宜一些，每个灯泡售价 35 美元。</p><p> LIFX 的移动应用程序无疑也是我们测试过的最流畅的。虽然这对您来说意义不大，但值得一提，因为移动应用程序是大多数人每天与智能灯互动的方式。主页显示了您家中的所有房间组，以及每个房间的灯的名称。您只需轻按一下即可轻松打开整个房间或特定的灯，并对智能家居中的所有灯执行相同操作。</p><p> LIFX 灯光支持调度，因此您可以对灯光进行编程以使其为您工作，这样您就很少（如果有的话）必须手动控制它们，而且还有大量的场景和效果可供选择。虽然我们尝试的所有彩灯都有预制的场景或预设，可以在应用程序中使用，但飞利浦 Hue 和 LIFX 显然是其中的佼佼者。就个人而言，我发现 LIFX 的场景和附加效果比 Hue 的更有趣、更吸引人。如果你想让你的客厅感觉有点像夜总会，你可以从“幽灵”或“柔和”等场景中挑选并使用“频闪”等效果。虽然大多数人可能不会定期使用这些小众场景和效果，但当您娱乐或只想为您的下一个电影之夜或游戏流媒体会话设置合适的氛围时，它们是非常有用的。</p><p> LIFX 在其生态系统中有<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYADPCWjJK-X-559-kI6ulGQTqZzglIKB8lkURHJg2M-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fstores%2Fnode%2F9029830011%3Fie%3DUTF8%26field-lbr_brands_browse-bin%3DLIFX">许多产品</a>，从标准的 A19 灯泡到灯带再到蜡烛。它也有开关，因此您可以根据需要物理控制智能灯。但飞利浦 Hue 也拥有所有这些选项，而且更多，不仅包括开关，还包括独立落地灯、户外聚光灯、筒灯、灯条和运动传感器。如果你想将家里所有的灯都转换成智能灯，并且有多种方式来控制它们，你将有更多的选择。</p><h2>最佳预算：TP-Link Kasa 智能 WiFi 灯泡</h2><p><core-commerce id="28d08bd389cd4a30a06f27bc4c4407b3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> TP-Link 的 Kasa 品牌以其坚固但价格实惠的智能家居设备而闻名，其智能灯也不例外。我们测试了<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUs4nz_l_NZXPfTFwuGgGq-hzPaiJLEsPQWCXOZyBmq9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FKasa-Smart-Changing-Dimmable-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB08TB8Z5HF">仅限 WiFi 的多色智能灯泡</a>，发现它们易于安装和使用，并且以实惠的价格提供了一系列功能；四包多色灯泡只需花费 40 美元。</p><p>除了安装过程简单之外，Kasa 的多色智能灯在我们测试的整个过程中都保持可靠连接，并且配套的移动应用程序简单明了。 All of the main functions for each light live in that bulb&#39;s dedicated page in the app, allowing you to change brightness, white levels, color, schedules and more without navigating through a bunch of different menus. Changing colors is nearly instantaneous, and the light changes as you drag your finger across the color wheel in the app. Editing the four presets you&#39;re able to save takes only a few taps, as does grouping multiple bulbs into rooms and creating lighting schedules. For the latter, if you do set on/off schedules, the app will show you the next step in that schedule (ie, off at 8:35pm) next to each individual light.</p><p> There&#39;s also a handy “usage” section in each light&#39;s page that shows you the bulb&#39;s energy use over time, plus an estimate of how much energy you&#39;re saving by using a smart light instead of a regular one. This is something that would be fun to observe over many weeks and months of using these bulbs, especially if conserving energy is one of the main reasons you invested in smart lights in the first place.</p><p> TP-Link claims you can connect “unlimited” smart devices to its mobile app, which technically means you can have as many Kasa smart lights in your home as you&#39;d like. We only tested a few together, so we can&#39;t say for sure how dozens of connected devices would affect app speed and light response time. These are WiFi-only bulbs, which means connecting them to a Zigbee hub isn&#39;t an option, so keep that in mind before deciding to invest in a house-full of these gadgets. It&#39;s also worth noting that these lights aren&#39;t compatible with Apple&#39;s HomeKit, although you can control them using Alexa and Google Assistant commands.</p><h2> Best all white: LIFX White E26 </h2><p><core-commerce id="fe0539056c8a4ed78f5993f35e4ff6ce" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Maybe you don&#39;t want to bother with colored lights. If that&#39;s the case, <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwODY1VFJENUw_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZ3MtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImMxN2RkNDJhLTI3YzktNGViYy1iZGMwLTlhNDNjNmQyNGMwOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAASTMwC65XBa7Qey988tEYbgemsv7y1T9uqIA_rsoF_fZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0865TRD5L">LIFX&#39;s White E26</a> is your best bet. You get all of the non-color features in the mobile app that we explained above, including schedules and virtual assistant controls, but in a more basic LED light bulb that only costs $10.</p><p> My biggest gripe is that it doesn&#39;t span the cool-to-warm temperature range that other white bulbs do. Rather, you&#39;re stuck with just one shade of white: 2700K, which is on the warmer side. This makes the LIFX bulb better for intimate settings like a bedroom or a living room, but since it&#39;s not overly warm, it could work in a home office, too. It&#39;s also dimmable, so you can control its brightness.</p><p> If you have a specific use case in mind for your smart lights that doesn&#39;t involve a rainbow of colors, then a LIFX bulb will more than suffice. They would work well in a child&#39;s room, for instance, allowing you to set wake-up and sleep schedules that gradually turn on and off the lights, or in a home office where you just want a bit more control over your lights without extra frills.</p><h2> Honorable mention: Sengled Smart Light Bulbs </h2><p><core-commerce id="92f4d2dcc31744cbaf23ec6326c0038d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1;pdid:Sengled’s Smart Light Bulbs" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Ftem4udG8vMzdMblIzZCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYzE3ZGQ0MmEtMjdjOS00ZWJjLWJkYzAtOWE0M2M2ZDI0YzA4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAWmb8zgPr91IGMRmGvp1wvtyNzvwNfBi26OOhm2PCKmH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F37LnR3d" class="rapid-with-clickid">Sengled&#39;s Smart Light Bulbs</a> deserve a shout because they&#39;re essentially more affordable versions of the best bulbs mentioned here, just with a few compromises. Key among those is that their colors are less nuanced than most others we tested and the mobile app is less polished.</p><p> That said, you&#39;re still getting millions of colors out of Sengled&#39;s smart lights and the app is easy to use. It also provides all of the features you&#39;d want from a smart light bulb, including grouping, schedules and automations. The fact that the Sengled mobile app isn&#39;t as slick as Hue&#39;s or LIFX&#39;s may actually work in its favor with newbies – the basic controls and labels will be very easy for smart home novices to understand.</p><p> The bulbs we tested were WiFi-based, so they do not require a hub. However, Sengled has a bunch of other smart lights that work via WiFi, Bluetooth or hub connectivity. A pack of four <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1;pdid:WiFi color bulbs" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Ftem4udG8vMzdMblIzZCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYzE3ZGQ0MmEtMjdjOS00ZWJjLWJkYzAtOWE0M2M2ZDI0YzA4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAWmb8zgPr91IGMRmGvp1wvtyNzvwNfBi26OOhm2PCKmH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F37LnR3d" class="rapid-with-clickid">WiFi color bulbs</a> will set you back $30, while a set of <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1;pdid:six Zigbee hub-based lights" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Ftem4udG8vM0pEWVlVNCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYzE3ZGQ0MmEtMjdjOS00ZWJjLWJkYzAtOWE0M2M2ZDI0YzA4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAQLCHg0VrqxrX9Y_bdZux3Npi8Q7lxcRrAhwRSoWjV9K&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F3JDYYU4" class="rapid-with-clickid">six Zigbee hub-based lights</a> costs only $100. Overall, Sengled&#39;s devices are much more affordable than Hue&#39;s, making them a good budget option regardless of whether you want to stick to WiFi or invest in a smart home hub like <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1;pdid:Sengled’s own" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Ftem4udG8vM3JqVUxQYSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYzE3ZGQ0MmEtMjdjOS00ZWJjLWJkYzAtOWE0M2M2ZDI0YzA4In0&amp;signature=AQAAASAAXVwMqjK1at0-rymLiUqpqxx3PAM9QYQDgkqPqUzX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F3rjULPa" class="rapid-with-clickid">Sengled&#39;s own</a> or a smart device like <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:13;pos:1;pdid:Amazon’s Echo" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Ftem4udG8vM0U3Wm5OdyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYzE3ZGQ0MmEtMjdjOS00ZWJjLWJkYzAtOWE0M2M2ZDI0YzA4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAeBrLoEwVSGRUrkGTh8vK54OtllAnKR53xpruRjS2AoA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F3E7ZnNw" class="rapid-with-clickid">Amazon&#39;s Echo</a> with a built-in hub.</p><h2> Best smart lamp: Philips Hue Signe Table Lamp </h2><p><core-commerce id="a94984eed06b413e85b92f51960923ec" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATR8PCTSgEP5CgXeRCYdH4ny9h9aQKuhjp3rjI9SoVXj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPhilips-Hue-573733-Gradient-Signe%2Fdp%2FB09BDKV84P">Philips&#39; Signe table lamp</a> is a slick way to add a wash of color into your living room, or a more controllable light source on your desk. The nearly two-foot tall lamp can be customized with up to three colors of light at once, plus it supports a full array of cool and warm hues as well. Shine it towards a wall to set the mood with colored lights during your game night, or use it to give yourself sufficient lighting during your next Zoom meeting – you can make it as fun or as practical as you need. It also supports effects like “candle” and “fireplace,” both of which produce moving light that emulates flickering flames. We also appreciate that the Signe lamp is a totally standalone device, like most of Philips&#39; new Hue bulbs: you don&#39;t need a Hue bridge to use it. But if you have one, you&#39;ll be able to do things like control the lamp when you&#39;re away from home.</p><p> The Signe lamp is a splurge, though, coming in at over $200. It&#39;s certainly worth it if you need just one powerful light source, but a more affordable alternative would be the <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfzYxyNRNEzxUYuRrTwQak0NkhzTtFMxSmw-W4AXwppl&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPhilips-Hue-Portable-Dimmable-Assistant%2Fdp%2FB00UVHAC1O">Philips Hue Go portable table lamp</a> . It too supports millions of colors and a full spectrum of warm and cool light, but it runs on a rechargeable battery and can be used wirelessly. Depending on the setting you choose, you&#39;ll get up to 18 hours of continuous use, making it a good option if you want a controllable light that can go anywhere you need it without fuss.</p><h2> Best smart light strip: Govee M1 RGBIC LED Strip Light </h2><p><core-commerce id="7f9b12877f2f4910947ee6b4e4a05a2c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Light strips can bring illumination to hard-to-reach places, or give a whole new vibe to your living room or office. The latest light strip from Govee, the <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfGgpxxsLTsxRxLGF9ATujGF3SNoCaPzAfu308bin0C1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGovee-Upgraded-Technology-Compatible-Christmas%2Fdp%2FB0B42BWVLM%2F">M1 RGBIC model</a> , gets super bright and supports a wide range of colors. It&#39;s WiFi-connected but requires no central hub, so even if you have other smart lights throughout your home, this one will fit in easily. One strip measures nearly 16.5 feet long and it&#39;s divided into 15 segments that you can control individually from within the Govee app.</p><p> We&#39;ll get into the app features, but it&#39;s worth noting where the M1 sits in the smart light strip space. There are various different lengths out there and you can even find some two-packs that will cover <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAS6nqE35DB4ZMEpBi5AZoQO6bfwbnes2MbktcOZOaWtn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDAYBETTER-Control-Bedroom-Decoration-Assistant%2Fdp%2FB09982KTLY%2F">up to 100 feet</a> . The 16.4-foot length is pretty common in single packs, although you can find some that run <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYP-Vg0iu988PGJl3uoHkExYlTL3FMPx2ygtHmhbCofw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGovee-Control-Segmented-Bluetooth-Changing%2Fdp%2FB099S9DXT7">up to 33 feet long</a> . You can expect to pay $25 to $50 for a basic, multi-color, 16.4-foot light strip and the price will go up from there depending on how many segments the strip has, the color range it supports, if it&#39;s WiFi-connected and other additional features. Govee&#39;s M1 Light Strip is on the higher end of the spectrum, coming in at $110 for 16.4 feet of light, but it still costs less than arguably its biggest competitor: Philips&#39; Hue Light Strips, which come in at <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9QaGlsaXBzLUh1ZS1CbHVldG9vdGgtTGlnaHRzdHJpcC1Db21wYXRpYmxlL2RwL0IwOENLSldTRlM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZ3MtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImMxN2RkNDJhLTI3YzktNGViYy1iZGMwLTlhNDNjNmQyNGMwOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAVU4xTfnggJbb54IFCX6ZX3PoPetCquQIsVjGf5G4vFI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPhilips-Hue-Bluetooth-Lightstrip-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB08CKJWSFS">$80 per 6-foot strip</a> .</p><p> I was impressed by not only the color spectrum the M1 Light Strip supports, but also how bright it is. This strip gets almost blinding, and I usually had it operating at just 75 percent of its full brightness. While you can&#39;t control each individual light on the strip, you can customize all 15 segments in the Govee app.</p><p> The sheer number of options and effects Govee provides is remarkable: the “effects lab” gives you pre-made basic colors, scenes that mimic sunrises, starry nights, different kinds of movies like thrillers and dramas, gaming genres and more. On top of that, you can make your own custom scenes (and choose to share them with others in Govee&#39;s Explore page) as well as your favorite colors and hues that you can save for frequent use. The strip&#39;s color is saturated and vibrant – combine that with the overall brightness and it was easily able to give my office an attractive, ambient glow when positioned around the periphery of my couch.</p><p> Aside from the higher price tag, my only other complaint about the M1 light strip is actually Govee&#39;s mobile app. It&#39;s a bit chaotic and takes some getting used to, so it might not be the best choice for anyone that wants something basic. However, I was able to get the hang of all the controls, and then some, after about a half hour. And you can always default to using Alexa or Google Assistant voice commands to control your light strip if you prefer, or you can set automations in the app that can take care of all your most used controls.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-led-light-bulbs-143022856.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-led-light-bulbs-143022856.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c17dd42a-27c9-4ebc-bdc0-9a43c6d24c08</guid><dc:creator>瓦伦蒂娜·帕拉迪诺</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 07 Jun 2023 19:15:03 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686165309</ingested><modified> 2023-06-07T19:15:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Lighting & Accessories]]></catego